{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/projects/designtools/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6b385cb5-7211-5017-8001-31fd9628fff9","excerpt":"得益于互联网行业的蓬勃发展，这几年设计工具如雨后春笋一般冒出。 随着竞争越来越激烈，产品迭代节奏也越来越快，而一款合适的设计工具能帮助设计师提高效率，把更多的时间专注于用户和业务上。为了能够帮助设计师更快地选择合适的工具，我做了 DesignTools…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/0b569/home.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"设计工具首页\"\n        title=\"设计工具首页\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/6af66/home.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/69538/home.png 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/72799/home.png 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/6af66/home.png 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/d9199/home.png 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/21b4d/home.png 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/f5c973d1b20b9ae978051cce112f3344/0b569/home.png 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>得益于互联网行业的蓬勃发展，这几年设计工具如雨后春笋一般冒出。</p>\n<p>随着竞争越来越激烈，产品迭代节奏也越来越快，而一款合适的设计工具能帮助设计师提高效率，把更多的时间专注于用户和业务上。为了能够帮助设计师更快地选择合适的工具，我做了 DesignTools，收集所有设计相关的工具，并详细介绍它们。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/0b569/detail.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"设计工具详情\"\n        title=\"设计工具详情\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/6af66/detail.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/69538/detail.png 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/72799/detail.png 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/6af66/detail.png 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/d9199/detail.png 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/21b4d/detail.png 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/d6a1121f1a8fc08efa1dd13c5bae1e6f/0b569/detail.png 2878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果你愿意的话，还可以和我分享你喜欢的设计工具。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/39148/submit.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"分享你的设计工具\"\n        title=\"分享你的设计工具\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/6af66/submit.png\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/69538/submit.png 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/72799/submit.png 320w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/6af66/submit.png 640w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/d9199/submit.png 960w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/21b4d/submit.png 1280w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/e15a3c5a40abba4cde3db2b176a2ac61/39148/submit.png 2876w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>你还可以用手机扫码在小程序上查询设计工具。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 258px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/0bbb8366d609764ae73cc09a1d3728c9/53f89/qrcode.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"设计工具小程序\"\n        title=\"设计工具小程序\"\n        src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/0bbb8366d609764ae73cc09a1d3728c9/53f89/qrcode.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/0bbb8366d609764ae73cc09a1d3728c9/0913d/qrcode.jpg 160w,\nhttps://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/leadream/juuun.io@gh-pages/static/0bbb8366d609764ae73cc09a1d3728c9/53f89/qrcode.jpg 258w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 258px) 100vw, 258px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>我发现很多设计师，尤其是刚入行的设计师，对设计工具存在一定认知误区。结合我的经验，我对设计工具有如下几点建议：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>没有最好的设计工具，只有最合适的。</li>\n<li>合适的设计工具能提高你的设计效率，但不一定能提高设计水平。</li>\n<li>如果它是你的生产力工具，且能支付得起的话，请尽量购买正版。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>谢谢阅读，希望能帮到你。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"我做了个设计工具集，帮你找到最合适的设计工具","date":"2019/06/07","description":"收集有用的设计工具。","color":"#FFF","cover":"designtools.png","demo":"https://designtools.cc","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/designtools/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/projects/designsystem/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计系统"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":